{"tid":2241516,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"(拋西瓜尋人PO)《魔瞳》一次換眼，讓我變成魔鬼（今年內都係完唔到 仲加1001唔開新POST）","createTime":"2020-10-13T11:03:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T18:03:20.000Z","uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8b4b4059c89317d2bdc1ab8d7ec163c586d3d721","tid":2241516,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:03:44.000Z","msg":"召喚BONNA樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1001又唔開埋新PO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><p class=\"center\"><strong><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qUjCYoy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqUjCYoy.jpg&h=ce70f042&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">網購《卷一》至《卷五》！：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2sRJZ7p\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2sRJZ7p&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbT44BXU%2FO%2BPkTPvsbUsuc1I%3D&h=902972b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2sRJZ7p</a></span><br />\n<br />\n簡介</strong></p><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n太古之初，天上唯一以六天創造大地，安息一天。當時的天使長路斯化，趁機率領天上三份一的天使，反抗天上唯一，可惜最後失敗收場。成王敗寇，這群天使最終被天上唯一以大能制服，折斷翅膀，剝奪「永生」的資格，並貶下凡間，成為魔鬼，以人類的慾望和負情緒為生。<br />\n<br />\n『魔瞳』，就是魔鬼眼睛的意思，而每個魔鬼，身上都必定會有一顆或以上的『魔瞳』。在一般情況下，『魔瞳』的外表和普通眼球沒分別，只有當魔鬼發動異能時，『魔瞳』的眼瞳顏色才會被魔氣刺激，變得赤紅。眼瞳的紅色越是鮮艷，表示那魔鬼體內的魔氣越是精淳。<br />\n<br />\n主角畢永諾，自幼生性孤癖，在十六歲的某天，他突然被一陌生男子強行塞上『魔瞳』，蛻變成魔。後來，他慢慢了解到，自己的命運天生就連繫著天下群魔，以及世界末日的秘密......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網購《卷一》至《卷五》<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2sRJZ7p\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2sRJZ7p&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbT44BXU%2FO%2BPkTPvsbUsuc1I%3D&h=902972b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2sRJZ7p</a><br />\n紙言<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.shikoto.com/i/sP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Fi%2FsP&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbT44BXU%2FO%2BPkTPvsbUsuc1I%3D&h=85c8fae1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.shikoto.com/i/sP</a><br />\nFACEBOOK 專頁<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/bonnaannob\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbonnaannob&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbT44BXU%2FO%2BPkTPvsbUsuc1I%3D&h=df5f9de0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/bonnaannob</a><br />\nPenana<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story.php?id=54188\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory.php%3Fid%3D54188&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbT44BXU%2FO%2BPkTPvsbUsuc1I%3D&h=8df9d17e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story.php?id=54188</a><br />\n<br />\n(歡迎追殺...)<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"902a6dc5e23b983dc1bbc92ed40d8522fd2cbe1a","tid":2241516,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:06:07.000Z","msg":"引用BONNA 上PO最新文章 扮有文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>#994  邦拿 &bull; 17 小時前<br />\n<br />\n有的放箭速度甚快，但準頭稍欠；有的命中率高，卻要花不少時間站好瞄準。<br />\n<br />\n唯有『慵』一人，能 一直氣定神閒，在打呵欠時仍可連環扣射，且百發百中。<br />\n<br />\n因此，在第一圈選拔後，我便已確定，『慵』是最適合的人選，就算她最終沒有成為『四騎』，我亦會將『赤弓』託付給她。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「最鋒利的箭，唯有搭上最精良的弓，才能完全發揮，<span class=\"red\">萬步穿心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>。」我看了看手中神器，又看向『慵』，認真地道：「不過，成為『四騎』，群魔便會以你馬首是瞻；手執『赤弓』你便得在戰場上交出相應『成績』。所以，你決定好了嗎？你能在這個稱為『現實』的夢，繼續廝殺嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n『慵』聞言，再次注視『赤弓』，默默不語。<br />\n<br />\n半晌，她才緩緩伸手，取過神器。<br />\n<br />\n『慵』看著『赤弓』，同時朝我淡然說道：「就算沒有『四騎』之名，沒有『赤弓』在手，我亦會竭力殺光在戰場上遇見的每一名天使。因為這樣子我才有機會延續與恩底彌翁的夢。」<br />\n<br />\n「我亦希望你能夠永遠續夢。」我微笑說道。看到她接下神器，我算是了卻一頭心事。<br />\n<br />\n「不過，這玩意倒適合我的性格。」『慵』一邊把玩『赤弓』一邊說道。<br />\n<br />\n「此話怎說？」我好奇問道。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"72deb91efca4b9cb9cfb66bd70a4a56eb7fb209c","tid":2241516,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:07:38.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RgXEsiP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRgXEsiP.gif&h=ac79855b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</p>"},{"pid":"96fe4155f3b47abe378cd92552ebca35a4104b16","tid":2241516,"uid":44674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T17:54:17.000Z","msg":"I&rsquo;m back"},{"pid":"25be0c70441b24e657304657f6be5310edb0000e","tid":2241516,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T18:03:20.000Z","msg":"此PO已死 不必再理"}],"pinned":{"pid":"25be0c70441b24e657304657f6be5310edb0000e","tid":2241516,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T18:03:20.000Z","msg":"此PO已死 不必再理"}}